      <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract: ">
                    Papers of the Justice of the peace, merchant.  Correspondence; financial papers and notes; 
genealogical notes; and school district records from Sharon, Vermont, 1820-1830; also a manuscript attributed to 
Albert Baldwin titled "Cultivating memory."</abstract>
